OL,3,C'Britain's wonkiest road' finally set
OL,4,Cto be repaired years after landslip
OL,6,FWork to repair a road in Wiltshire
OL,7,Fdubbed "Britain's wonkiest" will begin
OL,8,Fthis summer.
OL,10,FCouncillors voted unanimously in
OL,11,Ffavour of the plans on Tuesday 4 June,
OL,12,Fat a planning meeting at Trowbridge
OL,13,FCounty Hall.
OL,15,FThe "historically unstable" B4069 at
OL,16,FLyneham Banks, near Chippenham, was in
OL,17,FFebruary 2022, damaged the surface of
OL,18,Fthe road.
