OL,3,C'Britain's wonkiest road' finally set
OL,4,Cto be repaired years after landslip
OL,6,FParts of the road fell more than 25
OL,7,Fmetres down the hillside and the route
OL,8,Fdeveloped huge cracks with some BMX
OL,9,Friders even using it as a playground -
OL,10,F.
OL,12,FWiltshire Council said it had a "legal
OL,13,Fduty" to work on options to repair the
OL,14,Froad, and on Friday 10 May announced
OL,15,Fit has awarded the contract to rebuild
OL,16,Fit, along with drainage works, to
OL,17,FOctavius Infrastructure Limited.
OL,19,FOn Tuesday 4 June the project was
OL,20,Fgiven the final go-ahead.
