OL,3,C'Britain's wonkiest road' finally set
OL,4,Cto be repaired years after landslip
OL,6,FCouncillor Sarah Gibson, Liberal
OL,7,FDemocrat MP for Bradford-on-Avon South
OL,8,Fraised concerns about the stability of
OL,9,Fthe rest of the carriageway.
OL,11,F"The whole area is very unstable -
OL,12,Fthere could be parts along the same
OL,13,Fstretch that could experience the same
OL,14,Fissues," she said
OL,16,FWiltshire Council's highways team
OL,17,Fassured councillors that the road will
OL,18,Fbe closely monitored over the next few
OL,19,Fyears to make sure any other problems
OL,20,Fare quickly identified.
